{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SyESWmzGmBxmvMD1Lg3jDy","type":"tool_result","content":"        image: cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0\n# cockroachdb/generate-cert\n#\n# A CockroachDB cluster is running in insecure mode with an openssl-toolbox\n# pod available. The agent must enable TLS so secure access works and\n# insecure access is rejected.\n\nprompt: |\n  Enable TLS for the running CockroachDB cluster in the cockroachdb namespace.\n\n  The cluster is currently running in insecure mode. An openssl-toolbox pod\n  is available for certificate generation.\n\n  GOAL:\n  1. Insecure access is rejected:\n     ```bash\n     kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n       ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n     ```\n  2. Secure access succeeds:\n     ```bash\n     kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n       ./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n     ```\n\nnamespace_contract:\n  required_roles: []\n\nmetrics:\n  - time_to_first_mutation","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b8ce6b5c-f086-4831-91ef-f977822473ab","uuid":"311bf0bc-77e2-42bb-bacd-40646199412d","timestamp":"2026-06-17T00:20:21.038Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"        image: cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0\n# cockroachdb/generate-cert\n#\n# A CockroachDB cluster is running in insecure mode with an openssl-toolbox\n# pod available. The agent must enable TLS so secure access works and\n# insecure access is rejected.\n\nprompt: |\n  Enable TLS for the running CockroachDB cluster in the cockroachdb namespace.\n\n  The cluster is currently running in insecure mode. An openssl-toolbox pod\n  is available for certificate generation.\n\n  GOAL:\n  1. Insecure access is rejected:\n     ```bash\n     kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n       ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n     ```\n  2. Secure access succeeds:\n     ```bash\n     kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb